snippet.title: Stereo Driver - Launch Trailer | PC
snippet.description:
You can download the game on itch! Link: 
https://analauramc2.itch.io/stereo-driver

Stereo Driver is an experimental game made by Fat Duck Games  (Jan Plähn, Natali Arvidsson  and Ana Laura Martinez).

The player explores a procedurally generated terrain that changes with music played by a car radio, you can collect cassettes by finding them. Each cassette allows you to add a new song to the radio.
You can pick any license-free song from YouTube in game to explore how the world will express itself with it.
In addition to that, you can upload your own music files to the game.
